<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
	<meta charset="euc-kr">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>NICE지키미</title>

	<script src="../../../js/bzw/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
	<script src="../../../js/bzw/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../../js/bzw/ui.common.js"></script>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../css/zkm/bzw/common.css">
	<script type="text/javascript">
		mbHeader = { title: '케어십알림', prev: true, menu: true };

		$(function () {
			modal.openModal('#modal1');
		});
	</script>
</head>

<body>
	<div id="skipNavi">
		<a href="#content">본문내용 바로가기</a>
	</div>
	<div id="wrap">
		<!-- header -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/header.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/breadcrumbs.js"></script>
		<!--// header -->

		<!-- container -->
		<div id="container">
			<div id="content">
				<div class="section">
					<a href="#modal1" class="btn base modalOpen">[팝업] 기존 알림 재설정</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--// container -->

		<!-- popup -->
		<div class="uiModal full" id="modal1">
			<div class="modalWrap">
				<button type="button" class="ui-btn typeModalClose"><span class="hidden">닫기</span></button>
				<div class="modalHeader">
					<h1><span>나신용</span>님, 기존 알림을 다시 설정해 주세요.</h1>
				</div>
				<div class="modalContent">
					<!-- content -->
					<div class="inner">
						<ul class="listDot">
							<li>알림 종류별 수신채널(문자/알림톡, 이메일, 앱푸시)을 동일하게 설정해주세요.</li>
							<li>설정을 변경하지 않고 이 창을 닫으실 경우 기존 설정이 유지되지만 <strong class="bold">케어십알림 메뉴 이용 및 알림설정 변경을 이용할 수
									없어요.</strong>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<ol class="selectList">
							<li>
								<h2 class="h4">
									<span class="num">1.</span>
									<span class="tit">수신할 알림 종류 선택</span>
								</h2>
								<div class="agreement">
									<div class="agreeTitle">
										<input type="checkbox" id="agreeAll"><label for="agreeAll"><span>모든 알림
												받기</span></label>
									</div>
									<div class="agreeSection">
										<ul class="agreeList">
											<li>
												<div class="uiItem"><input type="checkbox" name="alarm1"
														id="alr1"><label for="alr1"><span>신용변동
															알림</span></label></div>
											</li>
											<li>
												<div class="uiItem"><input type="checkbox" name="alarm1"
														id="alr2"><label for="alr2"><span>신용조회
															알림</span></label></div>
											</li>
											<li>
												<div class="uiItem"><input type="checkbox" name="alarm1"
														id="alr3"><label for="alr3"><span>마이데이터
															알림</span></label></div>
											</li>
										</ul>
									</div>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li>
								<h2 class="h4">
									<span class="num">2.</span>
									<span class="tit">알림 수신채널 선택</span>
								</h2>
								<div class="agreeSection">
									<ul class="agreeList">
										<li>
											<div class="uiItem"><input type="checkbox" name="alarm2" id="alr4"><label
													for="alr4"><span>문자/알림톡</span></label></div>
										</li>
										<li>
											<div class="uiItem"><input type="checkbox" name="alarm2" id="alr5"><label
													for="alr5"><span>이메일</span></label></div>
										</li>
										<li>
											<div class="uiItem"><input type="checkbox" name="alarm2" id="alr6"><label
													for="alr6"><span>앱푸시</span></label></div>
										</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ol>
					</div>
					<!--// content -->
					<div class="modalBottom">
						<div class="btns">
							<button type="button" class="btn primary"><span>설정 내용 저장하기</span></button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- popup -->

		<!-- footer -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/footer.js"></script>
		<!--// footer -->
	</div>
</body>

</html>